{"tid":604873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警暈倒宿舍內 送院不治","createTime":"2018-03-25T06:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T00:20:33.000Z","uid":41404,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"41e841dfc2d330186d5981b586e07e466725f9c7","tid":604873,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"葵涌荔枝嶺道18號荔景紀律部隊宿舍，凌晨零時許，姓陳（54歲）休班警員，被姓李（53歲）妻子發現暈倒單位內，昏迷不醒，救護員接報到場，將陳送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理，惜經搶救後證實不治。警方經初步調查，相信事件並無可疑，事主死因有待驗屍後確定。據了解，休班警員本身有身體病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180325/57992595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F57992595&d=TIVvG9lqZBxrmq4oZvBTv7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=31e5a052\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F57992595&h=bf2155bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180325/57992595</a>"},{"pid":"b82d35d89332190066ed321465953d9ccfd7c085","tid":604873,"uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180325/photo/bkn-20180325111701286-0325_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180325134702\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180325%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180325111701286-0325_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180325134702&h=7ba7a6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n休班警員送院搶救後證實不治。(趙瑞麟攝)<br />\n<br />\n荔景紀律部隊宿舍一名休班警暈倒，送院搶救後不治。今晨零時許，葵涌荔枝嶺道18號荔景紀律部隊宿舍，一名姓陳（54歲）休班警員在家中昏迷，被姓李（53歲）妻子發現報警。事主由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院搶救後，惜告不治。警方經初步調查，相信事件並無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。暫列作有人暈倒送院時死亡處理。據了解，事主有身體病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180325/bkn-20180325111701286-0325_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180325%2Fbkn-20180325111701286-0325_00822_001.html&d=TIVvG9lqZBxrmq4oZvBTv7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6d0ec4b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180325/bkn-20180325111701286-0325_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"14519ac3ba9b2ebfebbb32b56fe3abaf4a659577","tid":604873,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"做差佬真係好易有暗病。<br />\n臨退休或者退休過一兩年就玩完。"},{"pid":"dfc310472a2a7ddfb696456984c4b2767c22346e","tid":604873,"uid":113626,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"14519ac3ba9b2ebfebbb32b56fe3abaf4a659577","tid":604873,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"做差佬真係好易有暗病。<br />\n臨退休或者退休過一兩年就玩完。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"生命 作賭注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9654ff06b8d0c6ef1dff879c4d4ec7e5c419439f","tid":604873,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e966d68bdd933abf47987f105d8986e8e5288c84","tid":604873,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfc310472a2a7ddfb696456984c4b2767c22346e","tid":604873,"uid":113626,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"14519ac3ba9b2ebfebbb32b56fe3abaf4a659577","tid":604873,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"做差佬真係好易有暗病。<br />\n臨退休或者退休過一兩年就玩完。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"生命 作賭注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"其實點解會咁? 輪班?"},{"pid":"402a40654f4ca8135444f5354c33de21d716e0c6","tid":604873,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:11:12.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐"},{"pid":"69dae804a4bc9ffc0acf262a4944d61376c13e6c","tid":604873,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e966d